  "purpose": "A long-running, multi-touchpoint relationship tracked between a contact (or constituents) and the organization or another contact. Distinct from Activity (single touchpoint) — Engagement is the longitudinal arc that activities accumulate inside. Used in mentoring programs, cultivation pipelines, case management, advocacy relationships, and any context where the relationship itself has lifecycle and outcomes.",
